Sentencas: In this study, AISI 430 stainless steel was coated with Mn-Co-CeO2 through electroplating technique.
Titulo: Investigation of oxidation and electrical behavior of AISI 430 steel coated with Mn-Co-CeO2 composite

Sentencas: To evaluate the oxidation behavior, isothermal and cyclic oxidation tests were used at 800 degrees C. Area specific resistance (ASR) of uncoated and coated specimens was also compared as a function of time during oxidation at 800 degrees C. Coating microstructure and oxidized samples were examined by scanning electron microscopy (SEM) and X-ray diffraction (XRD) device.
Titulo: Investigation of oxidation and electrical behavior of AISI 430 steel coated with Mn-Co-CeO2 composite

Sentencas: In isothermal oxidation, uncoated samples had more weight gain than the Mn-Co-CeO2 coated samples.
Titulo: Investigation of oxidation and electrical behavior of AISI 430 steel coated with Mn-Co-CeO2 composite

Sentencas: The coating layer improved oxidation resistance by limiting the diffusion of chromium cation and oxygen anion.
Titulo: Investigation of oxidation and electrical behavior of AISI 430 steel coated with Mn-Co-CeO2 composite

Sentencas: The cyclic oxidation results showed that the Mn-Co-CeO2 coated samples had a very good resistance to cracking and spallation.
Titulo: Investigation of oxidation and electrical behavior of AISI 430 steel coated with Mn-Co-CeO2 composite

Sentencas: Also, the results of ASR showed that formation of MnCo2O4 and MnFe2O4 spinels and also the presence of CeO2 resulted in reduction of area specific resistance.
